item.description:
@Barrage1 wrote:

[quote=“tehlobbiescape, post:1, topic:274240”]i need a simple compiling code, working on my new server
Not mod taharoks[/quote]Heres mine:

@echo off title YOURSERVERNAME if exist "%programfiles%\Java" (call :compile "%programfiles%\Java\") else (goto error) :compile for /D %%x in ("%~1jdk*") do (set p="%%~x\bin\javac.exe") if defined p (%p% -cp . *.java) if defined p (goto end) :error echo You do not have Java installed. Please download it at the site that is about to load. "%programfiles%\Internet Explorer\iexplore.exe" http://java.sun.com/javase/downloads/index.jsp :end echo Finished! echo Compiler By Denoria, From MoparScape! pause exit

Dont take out my credits please.
